        <li>

          Please reference the Airline PNR Number when communicating with the airline regarding this booking.</li>
        <li>

          Some airports have multiple terminals catering to domestic/international flights, please check the
          departure/arrival terminal of your flight with the airlines before reaching
          airport.</li>

      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="contact_information">
      <h4>Contact Information</h4>
      Delonix Travel Services
      dehradun (248001)
    </div>

  </div>
</div>